title: The Big Suey: Not A Mets Watch Along
description:
Daaaaaaaan, the Sunday Night NFL Postgame Show... is back. Presented by Gametime, Stu, Mike, Cote, Billy, and Juju break down Sunday afternoon's action while trying to hold Stugotz back from making it about the Mets. They discussed another head injury to a Dolphins QB, if Billy wants to recant his Josh Allen take, Kyle Brandt's thoughts on Russell Wilson, and an attempt from Mike to construct a top 5 throws in NFL history list on the fly.
